# Attention-grabbing format in responses

Use this format **only when attention is actually needed**, and **only at the very end** of your message.

**Format:** `# [emoji] **Short headline**`

- **H1** (`#`) makes the line large  
- **Bold** (`**text**`) adds weight  
- **Emoji** adds visibility (Cursor renders it; inline color/HTML does not)

